{"tid":1283921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑：有網台(暗指Myradio)煽惑衝擊，懇請年青人不要再相信！","createTime":"2019-07-04T03:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T10:02:55.000Z","uid":219007,"like":54,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"929a177559533fd6392ba76102a9c29a8e68e56b","tid":1283921,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"尋晚光明頂19指今次擺明空成計，引示威者入去，等你地天安門式聚人，到時俾中國判斷為緊急狀態出解放軍！<br />\n<br />\n好彩，年青人無聽某網台煽動，12點前撒離立法會，否則隨時性命難保！<br />\n<br />\n19擺明屌柒毓民，係佔領立法會期間就做毓民踩場，又話支持又話做得好，不停鼓吹鼓動，毓民仲屌陶傑怕死叫人唔好激嬲共產黨，而片頭片尾就剪埋佢以前係立法會話掟汽油彈既片段。<br />\n<br />\nMyradio擺明推人去死，毓民擺明想害年青人，難道毓民想見解放軍出城？<br />\n<br />\n19都叫你地唔好再信myradio ，毓民好明顯有古怪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a066588d21d507561f7c422a1ecc211fabbe0a","tid":1283921,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6156df1e03dc2906527394980676a17f772a2f","tid":1283921,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:25:01.000Z","msg":"入post講？<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民議會發言：香港除咗搞革命無第二條路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4cad37734cfd2c892b6ffe6e7ddde72dc32984b","tid":1283921,"uid":41477,"like":9,"dislike":15,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:27:39.000Z","msg":"成日叫人攻入立法會，<br />\n入左去三個鐘你毓民陳雲點解唔入去，<br />\n咁樣好明顯剩係得把口叫人去死。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iSjHxd7U5q0&amp;t=928